OL,7,FWatch the moment a lorry driver
OL,8,Fcrashed into the back of a learner.
OL,9,F(Credit: Liverpool Echo)
OL,11,FDashcam footage of the moment a lorry
OL,12,Fdriver crashed into the back of a
OL,13,Flearner because he "didn't notice
OL,14,Fstationary traffic" has been released
OL,15,Fby police.
OL,17,FIan Halliday, 45, was driving the HGV
OL,18,Falong Speke Boulevard in when he
OL,19,Fploughed into the stationary learner
OL,20,Fdriver.
