OL,7,FIn turn, the car crashed into other
OL,8,Fvehicles.JThe video shows the lorry
OL,9,Fdriver crashing into the black car in
OL,10,Ffront with force, causing the rear
OL,11,Fwindow of the vehicle to completely
OL,12,Fsmash and parts to come away from the
OL,13,Fcar.
OL,15,FDue to the force of the crash, the
OL,16,FAudi with L-plates was shunted into
OL,17,Fother vehicles. A blue Peugeot van can
OL,18,Falso be seen careering around another
OL,19,Fcar.
