OL,7,FAnother silver car ended up on a
OL,8,Fgrassy embankment with heavy damage to
OL,9,Fthe back of the vehicle.JAt the scene
OL,10,Fofficers found most people involved
OL,11,Fwere out of their vehicles and being
OL,12,Fchecked over by paramedics.
OL,14,FOne person had to be cut out of a car
OL,15,Ffollowing the crash, with firefighters
OL,16,Fremoving the roof.
