OL,7,FThe driver of the Audi was taken to
OL,8,Fhospital after she suffered several
OL,9,Fserious injuries. Other people were
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital, but police
OL,11,Fconfirmed they suffered minor
OL,12,Finjuries.JHalliday was later charged
OL,13,Fwith causing serious injury by
OL,14,Fcareless and inconsiderate driving.
OL,16,FHe appeared at Liverpool Magistrates'
OL,17,FCourt and was sentenced to 26 weeks
OL,18,Fimprisonment suspended for 12 months,
OL,19,Fon Thursday, 4 April.JHe also received
OL,20,Fa disqualification and was ordered to
OL,21,Fretake a test at a later date.
